'_1_create_inputs/batch/fifo_queue' is closed and has insufficient elements (requested 2, current size 0)

which indicates tensorflow-deeplab-resnet is trying to get elements from a queue after it is closed.

You should file an issue with tensorflow-deeplab-resnet, or even better, ask on StackOverflow.

body:
The first error seems to be

```
'_1_create_inputs/batch/fifo_queue' is closed and has insufficient elements (requested 2, current size 0)
```

which indicates tensorflow-deeplab-resnet is trying to get elements from a queue after it is closed.

You should file an issue with tensorflow-deeplab-resnet, or even better, ask on StackOverflow.
